{"tid":1474764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九龍灣連儂牆衝突　男子涉襲擊他人改簽保守行為","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:46:31.000Z","uid":230825,"like":30,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcb879c8ce6c8ebb9c55f6bfccab74c11464767","tid":1474764,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:40:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474858-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474858-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=61cb8256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474858-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd02de43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474858-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣連儂牆衝突　男子涉襲擊他人改簽保守行為<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-15 HKT 16:32<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名63歲男子因「連儂牆」問題，襲擊另一名男子，早前被控普通襲擊罪。（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n一名63歲男子因「連儂牆」問題，襲擊另一名男子，早前被控普通襲擊罪。案件今日於觀塘裁判法院再提堂，控方表示會撤控，改以簽保守行為處理。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁炳全報稱為肉檔東主，他准以1000元簽保，守行為1年，並須支付500元訟費。被告承諾未來一年不可對任何人、尤其是事主作出或企圖作出武力，或者威嚇使用武力的行為。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告上月11日於觀塘道‬近九龍灣巴士站附近的「連儂牆」觀看牆上內容時，因不滿一名男子撕掉牆上的告示貼，兩人起爭執，肉檔東主用腳踢向對方腹部。"},{"pid":"af0a632e8ebbf6d86620a00cbdebf891f5db358e","tid":1474764,"uid":230825,"like":29,"dislike":21,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"dllm 打完人無後果"},{"pid":"9ed0e950d07b17f67013edb76157927c606a71a3","tid":1474764,"uid":230825,"like":14,"dislike":16,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<br />\n食撚屎啦律政司！！！！"},{"pid":"fb2cb4c2c7752d77f5be038ca48e3c285ca5a359","tid":1474764,"uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:41:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"0a44cce6c5ae8bbb3dc8c2dd7d987666e2baf461","tid":1474764,"uid":23707,"like":6,"dislike":2