om/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474858-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdrXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=61cb8256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474858-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd02de43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474858-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣連儂牆衝突　男子涉襲擊他人改簽保守行為<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-15 HKT 16:32<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名63歲男子因「連儂牆」問題，襲擊另一名男子，早前被控普通襲擊罪。（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n一名63歲男子因「連儂牆」問題，襲擊另一名男子，早前被控普通襲擊罪。案件今日於觀塘裁判法院再提堂，控方表示會撤控，改以簽保守行為處理。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁炳全報稱為肉檔東主，他准以1000元簽保，守行為1年，並須支付500元訟費。被告承諾未來一年不可對任何人、尤其是事主作出或企圖作出武力，或者威嚇使用武力的行為。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告上月11日於觀塘道‬近九龍灣巴士站附近的「連儂牆」觀看牆上內容時，因不滿一名男子撕掉牆上的告示貼，兩人起爭執，肉檔東主用腳踢向對方腹部。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"連登仔乃全球最大型之吹水大炮群，最大特色乃:屌左先講！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3f0ab404e77433b378d9a129e52728dfa36503","tid":1474764,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人唔睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f6064e4786d801048b4daf3b0480a910835175","tid":1474764,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"個被告自己友黎架<br />\n<br />\n已經唔係第一個炒車post sosad"},{"pid":"1cd7f8fbabcba5638c0169f2eb10a11c35c67e57","tid":1474764,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"靠連登仔真係死得"},{"pid":"9808cf18c6155c00aee5b543cde5879199c8c821","tid":1474764,"uid":40276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:53:30.000Z","msg":"剩睇標題on99"},{"pid":"b3af20f306ceecfff5717f4ff84da2fc607fa277","tid":1474764,"ui